            "dates_of_birth_used": [
                "September 15, 1963"
            ],
            "caution": "<p>The FBI's Salt Lake City Field Office is assisting the Kootenai County Sheriff's Office in Idaho with the search for Donald Steven Lang. Lang is wanted for his alleged involvement in the sexual assault of a minor in Idaho between 2003 and 2007.\u00a0 Lang, a Canadian citizen, was last seen on his sailboat, ISHI, in Hawaii, in January of 2025.</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>On April 9, 2025, Donald Steven Lang was charged with\u00a0three counts of Lewd Conduct with a Minor Under Sixteen and one count Sexual Battery of a Minor in the District Court of the First Judicial District of the State of Idaho, in and for the County of Kootenai, and a state warrant was issued for his arrest.</p>",
            "nationality": "Canadian",
            "age_min": null,
            "age_max": null,
            "scars_and_marks": "Lang has multiple tattoos on his body including a faded conch shell with the word \"captain\" above it on his right arm.",
