            "details": "<p>The FBI's St. Louis Field Office is seeking the public's assistance in identifying the unknown individuals responsible for the murders of Marshun White and Marcus Price on September 19, 2024. The victims were shot and killed while sitting outside of their apartment building located at 1610 North Kingshighway Boulevard in St. Louis, Missouri. The two unknown suspects surveilled the victims for more than an hour before they ran up to the victims and shot them. The unknown suspects drove off in a dark-colored SUV.</p>",
